                        ],
                        "constructor" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "TagCinematic"},
                        "editorData" : [
                           {
                              "data" : [
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "AnimationTags"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "[REUSE] CROWD_Enthralled_Kneeling, SCENE_MOO_Audience_Altar_Kneel_LOOP_PLYR, HUM_F_Rig_SCENE_GOB_Orpheus_SuppressedKneel_LOOP_PLYR, HUM_FS_Rig_SCENE_CRE_AstralPrison_Daisy_Kneel_LOOP_DSY, [CUSTOM] In his calm and powerful yet commanding posture, the PLYR softens his body language when they see how terrified the woman is. He shifts his expression, from malice to \"benevolence\", as if he empathises and chooses “kindness” to rule. He slowly lifts his left hand up, fingers moving slowly yet surely, like a savior/saint's hand posture., [CUSTOM] From the default kneel pose, the WOMAN rocks her body, feeling terrified, trying to calm herself down. (something like fearful_kneel construction anim). She sees the PLYR noticing her and quickly averts her eyes away, with the context of \"oh crap! our eyes met! oh no no no no-\"    {Gwen Lee}"}
                                 },
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "Attitude"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "Default"}
                                 },
                                 {
                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "CinematicNodeContext"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "Among the awestruck, kneeling crowds, we focus on one woman in particular.She cringes and averts her gaze."}
