                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "AnimationTags"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "[CUSTOM] A child runs past the woman's back, holding a ball. His pet dog runs beside him., CUST_SweepBroom_01 anim conversion for maybe a person sweeping the floor., CROWD_HUM_F_Rig_CTZN_DFLT_CUST_InterestPoint_01/02/03 anim conversion for crowds browsing goods in the market., [REUSE] We can have 2 insert shots of bartering or laughter, and an establishing shot showing the market., [REUSE] Anims:, CINE_Slow_Walk_01/02/03, DFLT_CINE_ScratchNeckLeft_LHand_StandL_01, CINE_Laugh_01, {Gwen Lee}"}
                                 },
                                 {
