                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "[DUPE] Reuse the walk cycle from the node before, of the crowd, the WOMAN, and the CHILD, walking with rubble in their hands, with a blissful expression on their face., {Gwen Lee}"}
                                 },
                                 {
