                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "AnimationTags"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "[REUSE] CROWD_Enthralled_Kneeling, , [CUSTOM] From the pose before, the PLYR twitches his fingers and a psionic wave rushes through the crowd., [CUSTOM] From her panic kneeling mode, the WOMAN reacts to the psionic wave, she has the largest reaction in the crowd, and after some minor thrashing around and her holding her head, she slowly relaxes, arms limbing down gradually, and her movement slows down., [CUSTOM] From Enthralled_Kneeling, the crowd reacts to the psionic wave. (there'll be 2-3 variations for the reaction), {Gwen Lee}"}
                                 },
